Class ServiceConsumerStrategy<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wedriveu.mobile.service.ServiceConsumerStrategy<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the message consumed
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BookingConsumerStrategy

    public abstract class ServiceConsumerStrategy<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The ServiceConsumerStrategy abstract class that simply offers the message consumed through the dedicated BlockingQueue and let the subclasses define the RabbitMqConsumerStrategy#configureQueue(RabbitMqCommunication) implementation.
